statements: SELECT user_id, stress_level FROM StressData;
SELECT * FROM StressData WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT AVG(heart_rate) AS avg_heart_rate, MAX(stress_level) AS max_stress_level FROM StressData;
SELECT user_id, timestamp, stress_level FROM StressData WHERE timestamp > '2021-01-01';
SELECT user_id, body_temp FROM StressData ORDER BY body_temp DESC;
SELECT user_id, stress_level, heart_rate FROM StressData WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY heart_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM StressData WHERE stress_level > 5 AND body_temp < 98.6 ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, AVG(heart_rate) AS average_heart_rate FROM StressData GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT user_id, MAX(body_temp), MIN(body_temp) FROM StressData GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT DISTINCT stress_level, COUNT(*) AS num_records FROM StressData WHERE user_id IN (1, 2, 3) GROUP BY stress_level HAVING num_records > 2 ORDER BY num_records DESC;
SELECT * FROM stress_data;
SELECT id, user_id, stress_level, timestamp FROM stress_data WHERE stress_level > 5;
SELECT * FROM health_data WHERE temperature < 98.6;
SELECT user_id, MAX(heart_rate) AS max_heart_rate FROM health_data GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT * FROM stress_data ORDER BY stress_level DESC, timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, stress_level, timestamp FROM stress_data WHERE stress_level > 5 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, heart_rate, temperature, blood_pressure, timestamp FROM health_data WHERE heart_rate > 80 AND temperature > 98.6 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, stress_level, timestamp FROM stress_data WHERE user_id = 12345 ORDER BY stress_level DESC, timestamp ASC;
SELECT user_id, heart_rate, blood_pressure, timestamp FROM health_data WHERE blood_pressure < 120 OR heart_rate > 100 ORDER BY user_id ASC, timestamp DESC;

SELECT stress_data.user_id, stress_level, health_data.heart_rate, health_data.temperature FROM stress_data INNER JOIN health_data ON stress_data.user_id = health_data.user_id WHERE stress_data.stress_level > 7 AND health_data.temperature < 99.5 ORDER BY stress_level DESC, health_data.heart_rate ASC;
SELECT id, name, age, gender FROM users;
SELECT name, age FROM users WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT stress_level, stress_timestamp FROM stress_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM health_data WHERE heart_rate > 80;
SELECT user_id, max(heart_rate) FROM health_data GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT * FROM users WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY name DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, name, age FROM users WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT u.name, h.heart_rate FROM users u JOIN health_data h ON u.id = h.user_id WHERE h.heart_rate > 80 ORDER BY h.health_timestamp ASC;
SELECT u.name, s.stress_level FROM users u JOIN stress_data s ON u.id = s.user_id WHERE s.stress_level BETWEEN 5 AND 10 ORDER BY s.stress_level DESC, u.name ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT u.name, h.blood_pressure FROM users u JOIN health_data h ON u.id = h.user_id WHERE h.blood_pressure LIKE '%High%' ORDER BY u.name ASC, h.health_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM Stress_Data;
SELECT user_id, stress_level FROM Stress_Data WHERE stress_level > 5;
SELECT user_id, age, gender FROM User WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 30;
SELECT user_id, device_id FROM Stress_Data ORDER BY device_id DESC;
SELECT user_id, timestamp, heart_rate FROM Health_Status WHERE user_id = 1001;
SELECT user_id, timestamp, stress_level FROM Stress_Data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM User WHERE age > 30 AND gender = 'Male'
SELECT u.username, d.device_name, h.heart_rate FROM User u JOIN Device d ON u.user_id = d.user_id JOIN Health_Status h ON u.user_id = h.user_id WHERE h.heart_rate > 80
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS number_of_records FROM Health_Status GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5
SELECT u.username, u.age, h.blood_pressure FROM User u LEFT JOIN Health_Status h ON u.user_id = h.user_id AND h.timestamp > '2022-01-01'
SELECT * FROM Stress_Data;
SELECT stress_level, user_id FROM Stress_Data ORDER BY stress_level DESC;
SELECT user_id, MAX(stress_level) AS max_stress_level FROM Stress_Data GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id, stress_level FROM Stress_Data;
SELECT * FROM User_Profile WHERE age > 30 AND gender = 'Female';
SELECT * FROM Stress_Data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT User_Profile.name, Health_Data.heart_rate, Stress_Data.stress_level FROM User_Profile INNER JOIN Health_Data ON User_Profile.user_id = Health_Data.user_id INNER JOIN Stress_Data ON Health_Data.user_id = Stress_Data.user_id WHERE Stress_Data.stress_level > 5;

SELECT Device_Info.manufacturer, Device_Info.purchase_date, Health_Data.calories_burned FROM Device_Info INNER JOIN Health_Data ON Device_Info.device_id = Health_Data.id WHERE Health_Data.calories_burned > 500;

SELECT User_Profile.name, User_Profile.age, Stress_Factors.stress_cause FROM User_Profile LEFT JOIN Stress_Factors ON User_Profile.user_id = Stress_Factors.user_id WHERE Stress_Factors.stress_duration > 30;
SELECT DISTINCT Stress_Factors.stress_cause FROM Stress_Factors WHERE Stress_Factors.mood_at_end = 'Happy';
